A aim styled container map


Support:
Cubemaps, Custom Textures, Ambient Sound, 64 Spawnpoints

ChangeLog: (4/18/13)
  • [Removed] - Color Correction (x2)
  • [Added] - Custom texture
  • [Removed] - 2 Custom textures
  • [Removed] - Ambient_sound (enabled when shooting turtle)
  • [Fixed] - Light bleeding through displacement rock 
    

    SERVER REMAKES / EDITS ALLOWED
PLEASE ADHERE TO RULES
    


    #1. Leave all custom signatures in the map displaying either the creator i.e "SETHEN" or the "FireWaLLcs" community signatures. 

    #2. When renaming the map please DO NOT ADD V1, B2, final, or even fixed version as to I the creator, may in the future release a update version of this map which the same name.

    #3. The name of the map must remain the same to remove confusion but server names are allowed, only at the end of the map.  Example  my name for map"  zm an kaperas " /////  server name for map "  zm an kaperas PF ".
